---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="About Me."
	description="Interpretations of commodity futures by a student."
	pubDate={new Date('April 20 2026')}
	heroImage="/about-photo.jpg"
>
	<p>
		Welcome to Student Commodity Insights — a blog dedicated to breaking down commodity futures markets from a student's perspective.
	</p>
	<p>
		Here you'll find my personal interpretations and analysis of key commodity markets, including oil, natural gas, gold, wheat, and more. My goal is to make sense of market movements, trends, and news in a clear and straightforward way.
	</p>
	<p>
		This is not financial advice — just a student passionate about commodities sharing their thoughts.
	</p>
</Layout>
